{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01MHtjy1yApwmcJcrCcFSPZp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to generate 100 realistic fake OCR recipe text files. Let me break down the requirements:\n\n1. Save to: tools/title-loop/input/{RECIPE_TITLE}.generated.12.txt\n2. Recipe title in filename must match the main title in content (case-insensitive)\n3. Mix of English and Polish recipes (60/40)\n4. Variety: soups, mains, desserts, salads, appetizers, breads, drinks, preserves\n5. Multi-word titles (2-5 words), some single-word\n6. OCR noise: garbled lines, stray numbers, broken words\n7. Title position varies: top, after page number, after section header, mid-page\n8. Some with section headers like INGREDIENTS, SKŁADNIKI\n9. Different from existing recipes (provided list)\n10. 15-40 lines per file\n\nLet me start by:\n1. Creating a comprehensive list of 100 recipe titles (60 English, 40 Polish)\n2. Generating realistic OCR text for each\n3. Saving them to the correct location\n\nLet me think about the recipe titles first:\n\nENGLISH RECIPES (60):\n1. Classic Tomato Soup\n2. Chicken Parmesan\n3. Chocolate Cake\n4. Caesar Salad\n5. Bruschetta\n6. Sourdough Bread\n7. Coffee\n8. Strawberry Jam\n9. Beef Stew\n10. Apple Pie\n11. Garlic Bread\n12. Pasta Carbonara\n13. Fish Tacos\n14. Lemon Bars\n15. Mushroom Risotto\n16. Caprese Salad\n17. Pancakes\n18. Beef Wellington\n19. Tiramisu\n20. Minestrone Soup\n21. Grilled Chicken\n22. Brownies\n23. Greek Salad\n24. Mozzarella Sticks\n\n\n25. Ciabatta\n26. Iced Tea\n27. Mango Chutney\n28. Lamb Chops\n29. Cheesecake\n30. French Onion Soup\n31. Shrimp Scampi\n32. Shortbread Cookies\n33. Caprese Sandwich\n34. Spinach Dip\n35. Baguette\n36. Lemonade\n37. Peach Preserves\n38. Pork Tenderloin\n39. Carrot Cake\n40. Baked Salmon\n41. Oatmeal Cookies\n42. Vegetable Stir Fry\n43. Clam Chowder\n44. Chocolate Mousse\n45. Garlic Shrimp\n46. Focaccia Bread\n47. Orange Juice\n48. Apple Butter\n49. Duck Confit\n50. Crème Brûlée\n51. Grilled Vegetables\n52. Tomato Basil Soup\n53. Macarons\n54. Beef Bourguignon\n55. Raspberry Jam\n56. Croissants\n57. Iced Coffee\n58. Apricot Preserves\n59. Veal Piccata\n60. Panna Cotta\n\nPOLISH RECIPES (40):\n1. Barszcz Czerwony (Red Beet Soup)\n2. Piernik (Gingerbread)\n3. Żurek (Sour Rye Soup)\n4. Paczki (Donuts)\n5. Bigos (Hunter's Stew)\n6. Sernik (Cheesecake)\n7. Zupy Owocowe (Fruit Soup)\n8. Placki Ziemniaczane (Potato Pancakes)\n9. Pierogi (Dumplings)\n10. Makowiec (Poppy Seed Cake)\n11. Zupa Grochowa (Pea Soup)\n12. Babka Wielkanocna (Easter Cake)\n13. Zwoje z Miodem (Honey Rolls)\n14. Baczki (Mushroom Soup)\n15. Łazanki (Hand-Cut Pasta)\n16. Krakers (Crackers)\n17. Żurawina w Syropie (Cranberry Syrup)\n18. Kluski (Dumplings)\n19. Kielbasa (Sausage)\n20. Makownik (Poppy Seed Roll)\n21. Żur (Fermented Rye Soup)\n22. Ciastka Maślane (Butter Cookies)\n23. Chlebek (Small Bread)\n24. Żapa (Turnip Soup)\n25. Nalesniki (Crepes)\n26. Karpatka (Carpathian Cake)\n27. Konfitura Truskawkowa (Strawberry Jam)\n28. Kopytka (Hoof Pasta)\n29. Oscypek (Smoked Cheese)\n30. Paczuszki (Small Donuts)\n31. Grochówka (Pea Soup)\n32. Tort Sachera (Sachertorte)\n33. Drożdżówki (Yeast Pastries)\n34. Żurawina (Cranberry Preserve)\n35. Flaki (Tripe Soup)\n36. Babeczki (Cupcakes)\n37. Kompot (Fruit Compote)\n38. Jaja w Śmietanie (Eggs in Cream)\n39. Zupy Szpinakowe (Spinach Soup)\n40. Chleb Żytni (Rye Bread)\n\nI've got 40 Polish recipes listed. Rather than manually creating all 100 files, I should write a Python script to generate them systematically with realistic OCR artifacts like character substitutions and formatting errors.\n\nThe script needs to handle recipe titles, generate text with 15-40 lines per file, include OCR imperfections such as misrecognized characters and broken lines, add page elements like headers and footers, and save everything with proper filenames.","signature":""}],"stop_reaso